HEADWORD: Stadtholder
<hw>Stadt"hold`er</hw> <pr>(st⟦acr⟧t"h⟦omac⟧ld`⟦etil⟧r)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D. <ets>stadhouder</ets>; <ets>stad</ets> a city, a
town + <ets>houder</ets> a holder.]</ety> <def>Formerly, the chief
magistrate of the United Provinces of Holland; also, the governor or
lieutenant governor of a province.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

